EXTRACTED VALUE: It satisfies on many levels – easily accessible and involved gameplay coupled with great graphics and a cool story.
It’s one of those rare games where you know exactly what you are getting before you play it. You simply need to trust your instinct on this one.
This is one of those games where it can be a lot of fun to play with your friends and relive the experience that you had in arcades years ago.
What it may lack in revolutionary features it makes up for on the tracks where speed, skill, and surprises are not in short supply.
They have delivered what is most definitely a game for the fans, and that can't really be stressed enough.
